            "body": "Hi [~asuresh], [~kkaranasos] , really appreciate your comments and show\u00a0interest in this proposal. I'm working on the design documentation for this and will upload it in one or two days. Could you help review the doc and give your suggestions and comments to make it more\u00a0feasible?\u00a0",
