        "body": "Thanks for raising this [~Zian Chen]. We were actually experimenting something similar in YARN-6826. The difference being, we modify the scheduler to automatically allocate Opp containers when apps request above queue capacity.\r\nBut, yeah, demotion is definitely cheaper than promotion. It would also be interesting to make this scheduler agnostic. I would be interested in how this progresses. Let me know if I can help with reviews/code.\r\n",
